Description: Data exposed: Information on Biological Orders- Families- Species as well as species occurrence records and related dataThe data set currently contains information and linked data for: 19-230 Species- 1-671 Familes- 221 Orders. We have approximately 6-500 species observations- but are awaiting release on the majority of those.Also see TaxonConcept- where species are modeled differently.Size of dump and data set: 6.7 MB gzip
